snippet.title: The Mound: Omen of Cthulhu | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
In up to four player co-op, form a group of explorers searching for treasure. In this cursed jungle, danger is everywhere and monstrous creatures alter reality. Stay clear-headed and tame the jungle before it devours you…The Mound: Omen of Cthulhu will be coming in 2025 to PC, PS5 and Xbox Series X|S.
Wishlist now ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2569760/
